value: Resident, grassland, usually in montane areas: W, S and E (not C) South Africa, S Namibia (capensis); scattered in mts E Zimbabwe, N Malawi, Mozambique north to Kenya (mackinderi); Ethiopian highlands (dillonii).
mainly mountainous regions & hilly country with rocky areas, rocky gorges, also Karoo & open savanna

subcat_descr: Bill length (sex unknown) - Nares to tip
